          <h2 class="font-montserrat font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl text-[#1e3a5f] mb-6">How to Apply for a Chattel Mortgage</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 font-lato font-light leading-relaxed mb-4">Through Nik Finance, the process is straightforward. You need your ABN and GST registration details, identification documents, details of the vehicle or equipment you want to purchase (or a general description if still deciding), for full doc — 2 years of business financials and tax returns, and for low doc — 3–6 months of bank statements or recent BAS.</p>
